flowchart TB
    classDef edge fill:#f5efe6,stroke:#c9b89d,color:#2c2118,stroke-width:1.2px;
    classDef app fill:#fffaf4,stroke:#7b5e45,color:#241a14,stroke-width:1.4px;
    classDef core fill:#f6e4d2,stroke:#9a5b2a,color:#241a14,stroke-width:1.6px;
    classDef data fill:#f9f1da,stroke:#a07d2f,color:#241a14,stroke-width:1.4px;
    classDef ai fill:#efe3ec,stroke:#8b4d73,color:#241a14,stroke-width:1.4px;
    classDef ops fill:#e6efe4,stroke:#5d7b52,color:#241a14,stroke-width:1.4px;

    C[Customer]
    W[Winery Partner]
    T[Transport Provider]
    O[SwagriTech Ops Team]
    class C,W,T,O edge

    CF[Cloudflare<br/>DNS / CDN / WAF / Access]
    FE[Next.js Web App<br/>booking.swagritech.com.au]
    class CF edge
    class FE app

    UIState[Client State + API Layer<br/>Current: demo adapter<br/>Later: Azure APIs]
    class UIState core

    BQ[Booking Board<br/>multiple enquiries]
    PLAN[Itinerary Planner<br/>availability + route logic]
    WIN[Winery Controls<br/>slots / capacity / confirm mode]
    DISPATCH[Transport Planning<br/>live jobs + carrier match]
    OPS[Unified Ops View]
    class BQ,PLAN,WIN,DISPATCH core
    class OPS ops

    DB[(Tailor Moments Data Model<br/>bookings / wineries / jobs / partners)]
    M365[Microsoft 365 / Entra<br/>internal ops only]
    AZ[SwagriTech Azure Backend<br/>future integration target]
    class DB data
    class M365 ops
    class AZ core

    AI[OpenAI Layer<br/>ranking / suggestions / copilot]
    class AI ai

    NOTIFY[Email / SMS / Calendar Feeds]
    class NOTIFY edge

    C --> CF --> FE
    W --> CF
    T --> CF
    O --> CF

    FE --> UIState

    UIState --> BQ
    UIState --> PLAN
    UIState --> WIN
    UIState --> DISPATCH
    UIState --> OPS

    BQ --> DB
    PLAN --> DB
    WIN --> DB
    DISPATCH --> DB
    OPS --> DB

    PLAN --> AI
    OPS --> AI

    WIN --> NOTIFY
    DISPATCH --> NOTIFY
    OPS --> NOTIFY

    OPS --> M365
    M365 --> O

    UIState -. later .-> AZ
    AZ -. source of truth later .-> DB

    C -->|submits preferences| BQ
    W -->|sets availability| WIN
    T -->|accepts jobs| DISPATCH
    PLAN -->|creates itinerary| DISPATCH
    WIN -->|changes partner rules| PLAN
    BQ -->|select active booking| OPS
    DISPATCH -->|live route| OPS

    subgraph Journey[Operational Flow]
        J1[1. Customer creates enquiry]
        J2[2. Planner checks winery rules]
        J3[3. Best itinerary is produced]
        J4[4. Transport need is generated]
        J5[5. Ops monitors and resolves blockers]
        J6[6. Notifications go to partners and guests]
    end
    class J1,J2,J3,J4,J5,J6 edge

    BQ --> J1 --> PLAN --> J2 --> J3 --> DISPATCH --> J4 --> OPS --> J5 --> NOTIFY --> J6
